OL,3,CHorse and pony owners urged to
OL,4,Cvaccinate animals after discovery of
OL,5,Cequine flu
OL,7,FVets in the New Forest are encouraging
OL,8,Fall horse and pony owners to vaccinate
OL,9,Ftheir animals after the discovery of
OL,10,Fthe first ever case of equine flu in
OL,11,Fthe region.
OL,13,FThe case was recently confirmed in the
OL,14,Fnorth of the Forest, at Woodgreen, and
OL,15,Fit's now feared to be spreading
OL,16,Fthrough the herd of wild ponies that
OL,17,Froam there.
OL,19,FThe contagious respiratory disease can
OL,20,Fturn into fatal pneumonia if left
OL,21,Funtreated.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
