OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1781082348
OL,3,CHorse and pony owners urged to
OL,4,Cvaccinate animals after discovery of
OL,5,Cequine flu
OL,7,FLocal vet Alan Hough has spent the
OL,8,Fpast few weeks providing booster
OL,9,Fvaccinations to horse owners across
OL,10,Fthe New Forest.
OL,12,FHe said: "Unfortunately, it wouldn't
OL,13,Fbe practical or feasible to try and
OL,14,Fvaccinate the wild herd of five and a
OL,15,Fhalf thousand animals.
OL,17,F"So, the way we protect them is by
OL,18,Fensuring that all the other equines
OL,19,Fthat border the New Forest, that ride
OL,20,Fout in the New Forest, that visit the
OL,21,FNew Forest are vaccinated.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1781082348
OL,3,CHorse and pony owners urged to
OL,4,Cvaccinate animals after discovery of
OL,5,Cequine flu
OL,7,F"So therefore by herd immunity we
OL,8,Fadminister immunity to those animals
OL,9,Fin the forest."
OL,11,FThe virus can travel up to 5km in the
OL,12,Fair which means there is a high risk
OL,13,Fthat other ponies and animals using
OL,14,Fthe New Forest will become infected.
OL,16,FVerderers in the New Forest are
OL,17,Fadvising riders to avoid livestock and
OL,18,Fcommunal water troughs.
OL,20,FSymptoms of Equine Flu according to
OL,21,Fthe animal charity Blue Cross
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
