OL,3,CHorse and pony owners urged to
OL,4,Cvaccinate animals after discovery of
OL,5,Cequine flu
OL,7,FA college in Bransgore for students
OL,8,Fwith special educational needs is
OL,9,Fensuring that all of their 29 horses
OL,10,Fare up to date with vaccinations and
OL,11,Fboosters.
OL,13,FSuzi Barnett, who works at The Fortune
OL,14,FCollege, said: "All of our horses have
OL,15,Ftheir own individual care plans,
OL,16,Fsimilarly to our students and with
OL,17,Fthat we are monitoring their
OL,18,Ftemperature, their pulse, their
OL,19,Frespiration regularly.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
