CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1781082348
OL,3,CHorse and pony owners urged to
OL,4,Cvaccinate animals after discovery of
OL,5,Cequine flu
OL,7,F"We have increased that monitoring and
OL,8,Fall of our students are involved
OL,9,Fwithin that monitoring, so they are
OL,10,Flearning to monitor their own health,
OL,11,Falong with the horses health.
OL,13,F"So while it is a challenge at the
OL,14,Fmoment, we are utilising the
OL,15,Fopportunity to teach our young people
OL,16,Fabout these issues in life."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
